The BIGGEST physical ECO logo of all! Its diameter is 358 meters, and the length of all lines is 2.51 kilometers! 
The creation of the logo took 25 minutes and 1.5 hours of preparation to plot the route on the ground.
I had to walk through deep puddles, climb over fences and overcome deep ravines in wet snow! 
It was an unforgettable and amazing experience!Especially when all ordinary people are walking along the paths, and at this time the ECO enthusiast are moving along their own trajectories!
I know, that here we can see much bigger logos and much more creative, but its the biggest that i could create in the real life with the lack of time.

#📦008-largest-physical-logo @Andy | Eco @Andrew | Eco @Henry  |  Eco @Sergey (ICO Drops) 
We are happy to introduce you the world's largest Eco logo.

We thought for a long time about where and how we can make Eco's logo and found out that we have the third-largest Ferris wheel in Russia in our city.
On ordinary days, a simple animation spins on the wheel.
Long story short, we contacted the Ferris wheel administration and they agreed to display Eco's logo and name on it. 
We love Eco because it brings us back to childhood and encourages us to do fun things. Thanks, Eco! 🤙

Location: Novosibirsk city, Siberia, Russia
https://goo.gl/maps/yDw9kNsN5QkLkQg2A
Ferris wheel height: 67 meters
Logo diameter: 60 meters

All effects are made from original footage.
Original footage from different angles here:
https://www.dropbox.com/sh/bt228d0np6xshcm/AAAx9AhIoLPSWiy1DjFdByMba?dl=0
